{"tid":1381410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沈旭暉: 港澳辦記者會比過去兩個月宣傳溫和","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:41:16.000Z","uid":121713,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cc04014250136c19a15bea4521edb04027aeb627","tid":1381410,"uid":121713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:33:10.000Z","msg":"港澳辦記者會，比過去兩個月宣傳溫和，一半是依循港英對六七的處理：<br />\n1. 深層次問題是發展、經濟，各階層發大財，就能和諧穩定<br />\n2. 靠支持警隊，能解決目前街頭運動<br />\n3. 政治制度、政改、駐軍等一概迴避，希望一切維持現狀<br />\n4. 沒有嚴斥外國勢力、顏色革命、港獨，以免局勢進一步國際化<br />\n<br />\n解讀：<br />\n1. 北京鼓勵特區政府派錢、派福利、搞基建<br />\n2. 北京目前定性是治安問題，即使持續，也不構成管治危機<br />\n3. 北京相信隨著運動激化，香港主流輿論會慢慢改變，希望各界領袖表態支持維護法治的警隊<br />\n4. 北京目前不鼓勵極左意識形態，因為變數太大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇黎共匪唔會強硬回應，勇武巴打+和理非都仲有大把空間升級"},{"pid":"5ab0b6e51d8f89dc7d75c38f392652e9afba9b87","tid":1381410,"uid":57677,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"折招：引警犬港共犯錯"},{"pid":"012295f95d26246254e04a202885843b333df91d","tid":1381410,"uid":107297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:02:53.000Z","msg":"有道德底線先可以令人罷工<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsbkoS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsbkoS</a>"},{"pid":"312d27ec4493f4b57dc6f9a16cf3eeaf21312761","tid":1381410,"uid":61280,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港澳辦記者會，比過去兩個月宣傳溫和，一半是依循港英對六七的處理：<br />\n1. 深層次問題是發展、經濟，各階層發大財，就能和諧穩定<br />\n2. 靠支持警隊，能解決目前街頭運動<br />\n3. 政治制度、政改、駐軍等一概迴避，希望一切維持現狀<br />\n4. 沒有嚴斥外國勢力、顏色革命、港獨，以免局勢進一步國際化<br />\n<br />\n解讀：<br />\n1. 北京鼓勵特區政府派錢、派福利、搞基建<br />\n2. 北京目前定性是治安問題，即使持續，也不構成管治危機<br />\n3. 北京相信隨著運動激化，香港主流輿論會慢慢改變，希望各界領袖表態支持維護法治的警隊<br />\n4. 北京目前不鼓勵極左意識形態，因為變數太大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇黎共匪唔會強硬回應，勇武巴打+和理非都仲有大把空間升級</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚又扮高啦教棍共狗，一句到尾你狗党慣技：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n扮豬劏老虎，時間買空間！！！</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"916f11cc49276ef2dd88bfc1c5b30438d90ea117","tid":1381410,"uid":87116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:03:17.000Z","msg":"［禍不及妻兒］Pokemon Go式全民搵仔（再開過）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1376102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1376102</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"440ebdd3d948b0bafe2a9ffd95e09f7c68b07a97","tid":1381410,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"台詞照舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算吧喇"},{"pid":"ecd96ccd160dcc3580a5597fed903246c2ad7d83","tid":1381410,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:05:55.000Z","msg":"be water 最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440301c1f8e7c958bf20dac67838dd318c18e35a","tid":1381410,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:07:11.000Z","msg":"聽完會講得：屌，又係嗰啲嘢！<br />\n但沈旭暉有佢道理"},{"pid":"a1faa160934c6e9b386f4eae8ba9485f46c44b6f","tid":1381410,"uid":205346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:13:13.000Z","msg":"解讀：<br />\n1.繼續追擊警黑作為長期運動嘅火藥，文宣要做好，唔可以俾黑警翻身<br />\n2.旗幟鮮明愛國，打着紅旗反紅旗"},{"pid":"73932217a2a5f1cdf0b597d653cada82ab2ad8e7","tid":1381410,"uid":265019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gbBOsE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gbBOsE.jpg&h=84e47f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34q3tsE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34q3tsE.png&h=61c2aced&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe43224cf1e91b4a0bb2251ab2eb08411e087ebc","tid":1381410,"uid":257368,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:15:44.000Z","msg":"佢同港共個方式係一致<br />\n冷處理 唔回應 拖到你自己內部矛盾/9月收皮"},{"pid":"cfab91bbbb195998901683617842483dbab3ed4d","tid":1381410,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">老解呢老解呢</span></span>"},{"pid":"a85a00ce359c8ca1ffafe3d9a044ff92c8d61ae8","tid":1381410,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"我同你班廢青講，依家已經冇辦法阻止官商鄉黑警<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382832</a><br />\n互推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957e0b0b362b4b7c46ff6f03c5b4a3fae4a3a3b5","tid":1381410,"uid":237425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5ab0b6e51d8f89dc7d75c38f392652e9afba9b87","tid":1381410,"uid":57677,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"折招：引警犬港共犯錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:07:42.000Z","msg":"其實已經錯到好多步<br />\n<br />\n爭最後一根稻草令狗隊兵變或犯下彌天大錯.....<br />\n希望唔係後者，唔想有義士出事"},{"pid":"244319111ca1512013759ad354d7de417b012c4a","tid":1381410,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"堅離地城：沈旭暉國際生活台 Simon's Glos World<br />\n28分鐘 &middot; <br />\n我地每做一件事，都要define target audience，正如呢個page從來唔以兩極為target audience。港澳辦個 press con，大家覺得好悶好正常，因為 target audience根本唔係香港人，亦唔係國際媒體，只係好niche既「一小撮人」。<br />\n<br />\n記者會既重要性，在於制度化，令「北京直接就香港問題發表正式意見」變成一個制度，replace左週街放風既「消息人士」，同埋大大小小有唔同線路既親北京媒體。呢次press con明確定性香港發生既事係「內部問題」，唔出解放軍，仲要派無人認識既發言人出場、唔出主任，就係話其實發生既野，相對中美貿易戰呢D大事，都仲係好mild，可以自己拆掂，target audience正係不斷謊報軍情、唯恐天下不亂、日日警告出兵、不斷上綱上線既「別有用心人士」，叫佢地唔好「搞亂香港」。由於釋放左出兵既tension，繼續鼓吹出兵既「愛國人士」，就變左endorse焦土，暫時會收斂一下；兩極無左域外一極，得返功能性既警察，北京自然期望另一極既grand momentum，亦會慢慢失焦。以上です。<br />\n<br />\nPS：記者朋友，我每次訪問堅要申報。發夢Facebook另計。"},{"pid":"fa1fea3a94ac77ca2a0a58c85906c36718bc3126","tid":1381410,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:38:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdce3305eba6e3db3b4054254ab7c35f352045e4","tid":1381410,"uid":283157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}